result.name: Vivant TKR

reviews.text: great atmosphere, great wine selection in a reasonable price, and food were excellent.  not to mention the owner is expert in champagne amd very friendly too.  highly recommend

Great selection of wine and champagne at very reasonable prices! Marston knows his champagne and Burgundy wines, very helpful and friendly. Food is amazing, if you love lamb then you must try! The beef is actually yak and recently add duck to the menu.
Delicious exotic cuisine, delightful décor!

Nice place with Western atmosphere, American & Italian dishes.

A good lemon tea there!

Hamburger, pasta, pizza are served there, but the rice of the risotto is a little undercooked. Ate two times risotto for being sure of the rice's cooking but I was disappointed. 

It is not cheap while the location is not near a MTR station. 

But good atmosphere there and well decorated place. Liked the mood.

I don't like so much the air-conditionner was so cold each time I went.

If you want to dinner there, please book a table before coming. There are full some nights! Especially the Friday and Saturday nights.
Excellent place
